Class MathUtil

java.lang.Object
  org.cloudbus.cloudsim.util.MathUtil

public class MathUtil
extends java.lang.Object

A class containing multiple convenient math functions. To use some of the function you must download Michael Thomas Flanagan's Java Scientific Library: http://www.ee.ucl.ac.uk/~mflanaga/java/

Since:
CloudSim Toolkit 3.0
